    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062780/extras/f5eeb61564d080845b5abf9cba958b38.poster.avif?t=1771513789\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062780/extras/f5eeb61564d080845b5abf9cba958b38.webm?t=1771513789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062780/extras/f5eeb61564d080845b5abf9cba958b38.mp4?t=1771513789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Phil's Contract</strong> is a 2D platformer with fast-paced movement with an emphasis bunny-hopping and beat 'em up-esque combat. Featuring charming, yet grimy pixel art inspired from the likes of flash animations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a short, stubby cursed office worker from hell who wants nothing but to be free. Being very dissatisfied with his current standing, and having to do the same bullshit menial tasks over and over again, he SNAPS and escapes from hell. Only for his boss to get extremely fucking pissed and putting a curse on where Phil resides, turning everything against him. He must break the curse and destroy the contract in which it all began..</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Currently the demo includes the first level, &quot;The Outside&quot;, with more content being planned in subsequent updates until the release of the final game.</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THOU ART OUT... FOR BLOOD.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully animated cutscenes,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New movesets to keep the experience fresh and unique as you play as 3 characters throughout the story,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT the characters you play as Phil. Face them to gain their trust.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique soundtrack.</p></li></ul>",
